---
import AdminLayout from '../../layouts/AdminLayout.astro';
---

<AdminLayout title="E-mail">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="mb-8 flex items-center justify-between gap-4 flex-wrap">
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">E-mail</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">E-mailklient til administrerede postkasser</p>
      </div>
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-medium bg-amber-50 text-amber-800 border border-amber-200 rounded-full px-3 py-1.5">
        Kræver operatørtrin
      </span>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><rect x="2" y="4" width="16" height="12" rx="2" stroke="#3b82f6" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M2 7l8 5 8-5" stroke="#3b82f6" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-1">E-mailklienten er ikke aktiveret endnu</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-blue-700 mb-3">
            Denne side er implementeringsklar, men e-mailruter (<code class="bg-blue-100 px-1 rounded">/email/config</code>, <code class="bg-blue-100 px-1 rounded">/email/folders</code> m.fl.) er ikke tilgængelige i API-laget endnu. Operatøren skal fuldføre opsætningen nedenfor, inden klienten kan aktiveres.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xs text-blue-600 font-medium">Status: <span class="text-amber-700">Afventer operatøropsætning</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl divide-y divide-gray-100">
      <div class="px-6 py-5">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Trin 1 — Kør databaseskema (cPanel phpMyAdmin)</p>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs text-gray-700 mb-2">api/src/schema_email_client.sql</div>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Opretter <code class="bg-gray-100 px-0.5 rounded">email_accounts</code>, <code class="bg-gray-100 px-0.5 rounded">email_folders</code>, <code class="bg-gray-100 px-0.5 rounded">email_messages</code>, <code class="bg-gray-100 px-0.5 rounded">email_drafts</code>. Kør på hvert klient-DB, hvor e-mail skal aktiveres.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="px-6 py-5">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Trin 2 — Tilføj env-variabler (api/.env)</p>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs text-gray-700 space-y-1">
          <div>EMAIL_IMAP_HOST=mail.klientdomæne.dk</div>
          <div>EMAIL_IMAP_PORT=993</div>
          <div>EMAIL_IMAP_SSL=true</div>
          <div>EMAIL_SMTP_HOST=mail.klientdomæne.dk</div>
          <div>EMAIL_SMTP_PORT=587</div>
          <div>EMAIL_SMTP_SSL=true</div>
          <div>EMAIL_ENCRYPTION_KEY=&lt;32-byte hex — openssl rand -hex 32&gt;</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="px-6 py-5">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Trin 3 — Wire API-ruter (server/src/routes/)</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 mb-3">Følgende seks ruter skal implementeres i Agent Enterprise API-laget (udenfor dette mappe-scope):</p>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs text-gray-700 space-y-1">
          <div>GET  /email/config</div>
          <div>GET  /email/folders</div>
          <div>GET  /email/messages?folder_id=</div>
          <div>GET  /email/messages/:id</div>
          <div>POST /email/drafts</div>
          <div>POST /email/send</div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2">Se <code class="bg-gray-100 px-0.5 rounded">PHASE6_HANDOFF.md</code> for den fulde rutekontrakt og svar-format.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="px-6 py-5">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Trin 4 — Genstart Node.js-app</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-600">cPanel &rsaquo; Setup Node.js App &rsaquo; Restart</p>
      </div>

      <div class="px-6 py-5">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Verifikation</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-600">Når ovenstående trin er fuldført og ruterne er wired, vil e-mailgrænsefladen være tilgængelig i admin-panelet. Der kræves ingen yderligere kodeændring i dette repo.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</AdminLayout>
